## Install Kali ##

## Install Tools ##
# Install Juice Shop #
  git clone HTTPS://github.com/juice-shop folder
  Sudo apt install nodejs
  sudo  npm install –force
  Install FoxyProxy for web browser. It’s a plugin. Configure for ip 127.0.0.1
  Install Sublist3r
  sudo apt install sublist3r



Enumeration

Information on domain links
sublist3r -d irobot.com
search crt.sh website for domain information, %.irobot.com 


